{"tid":2152586,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭入稟追租　凱施餅店3050萬低價沽筲箕灣舖「填氹」","createTime":"2020-08-12T05:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T05:32:08.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ccd48955b85de41e2d4d6d3d78ef6f65605225f7","tid":2152586,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T05:29:20.000Z","msg":"零售市況受新冠肺炎疫情嚴重拖累，生意一落千丈，上半年部分分店曾被業主入稟追租的本地老牌餅店凱施餅店，周一（3日）才以意向價3,300萬元，放售作為收租用途的筲箕灣舖位，惟不足5天，減價250萬元或7.6%，以3,050萬元極速沽出。<br />\n<br />\n市場消息透露，上述舖位為筲箕灣道388至414號地下H1舖，建築面積約800方呎，本周一才委託代理放盤，隨即獲多名買家洽購，終以約3,050萬元沽出，呎價38,125元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/508072/%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A9%E6%80%A5%E8%AE%93-%E9%81%AD%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E8%BF%BD%E7%A7%9F-%E8%80%81%E7%89%8C%E9%A4%85%E5%BA%973050%E8%90%AC%E4%BD%8E%E5%83%B9%E6%B2%BD%E7%AD%B2%E7%AE%95%E7%81%A3%E8%88%96-%E5%A1%AB%E6%B0%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F508072%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%25AE%2593-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25A8%259F%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E7%25A7%259F-%25E8%2580%2581%25E7%2589%258C%25E9%25A4%2585%25E5%25BA%25973050%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BD%258E%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25B2%25BD%25E7%25AD%25B2%25E7%25AE%2595%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%2588%2596-%25E5%25A1%25AB%25E6%25B0%25B9&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfwaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=4548c44f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/508072/%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A9%E6%80%A5%E8%AE%93-%E9%81%AD%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E8%BF%BD%E7%A7%9F-%E8%80%81%E7%89%8C%E9%A4%85%E5%BA%973050%E8%90%AC%E4%BD%8E%E5%83%B9%E6%B2%BD%E7%AD%B2%E7%AE%95%E7%81%A3%E8%88%96-%E5%A1%AB%E6%B0%B9</a>"},{"pid":"bfd3da8dc391c870223a809392c85a023d6f6fd1","tid":2152586,"uid":138502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T05:32:08.000Z","msg":"藍店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\